{"tid":1308132,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[中文]CCCU/UOW vs HKCC vs SYU","createTime":"2019-07-11T21:40:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T00:43:29.000Z","uid":176565,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4afaf7bc7e88c34b191adade80b1df950bf0bf72","tid":1308132,"uid":176565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T21:40:29.000Z","msg":"CCCU(或者應該改名叫UOW<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n今年新出左個自資課程<br />\n叫「中國語言文學及傳意（榮譽）文學士」<br />\n今日去左in佢都收左我<br />\n但諗諗下CCCU今年賣左盤<br />\n加上新開課程白老鼠好似好伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nHKCC就已經有offer<br />\n但我數學得2唔想讀數<br />\n加上asso讀中文好似好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以對HKCC都有啲卻步<br />\n<br />\nSYU就暫時都仲諗緊去唔去in<br />\n依家仲心大心細咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人解答到我讀邊間好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b024692048e0fa141996f8d0137de21957cef1","tid":1308132,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:57:13.000Z","msg":"太空第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其他幾間中文都係垃圾"},{"pid":"b510e7495a8c81cb00d0539631881140997b6e8e","tid":1308132,"uid":176565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071d4e32fbeff9d9108a0c5d015f429c43028168","tid":1308132,"uid":176565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}